{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/TIL_49_210310/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"22-css-grid-basic-concepts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#22-css-grid-basic-concepts\" aria-label=\"22 css grid basic concepts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[2.2] CSS Grid Basic Concepts</h1>\n<h3 id=\"grid\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grid\" aria-label=\"grid permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grid</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Grid가 나온 이유?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>각 item 간의 간격 등을 grid 형태로 깔끔하게, 정돈되게 관리할 수 있음</li>\n<li>flex box에서는 개별 item 간의 간격을 각각 조정해줘야 하는 귀찮음</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Grid는 flexbox와 마찬가지로 father element에 적용</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"1-grid-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-grid-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"1 grid 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Grid 방법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">display : grid</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-grid의-column-사이즈-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-grid%EC%9D%98-column-%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"2 grid의 column 사이즈 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Grid의 column 사이즈 설정</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">grid-template-columns : 250px 200px 100px</code></li>\n<li>원하는 컬럼 수만큼 사이즈를 넣어주면 됨</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-grid-row-사이즈-성정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-grid-row-%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88-%EC%84%B1%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"3 grid row 사이즈 성정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Grid row 사이즈 성정</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">grid-template-rows : 250px 200px 100px</code></li>\n<li>원하는 row 수만큼 사이즈를 넣어주면 됨</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-column-row-간의-간격-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-column-row-%EA%B0%84%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%84%EA%B2%A9-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"4 column row 간의 간격 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. column, row 간의 간격 설정</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">gap : 20px</code> : 행, 열 모두 간격 동시 설정</li>\n<li>column-gap</li>\n<li>\n<p>row-gap</p>\n<ul>\n<li>각각의 간격 별도 설정</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"23-grid-template-areas\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#23-grid-template-areas\" aria-label=\"23 grid template areas permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[2.3] Grid Template Areas</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Grid로 Layout을 설계 하는 방법</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"grid-template-areas\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grid-template-areas\" aria-label=\"grid template areas permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>grid-template-areas</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>의미 : grid로 화면의 전체 layout을 설정할 수 있도록 한다.</li>\n<li>grid 상에서, 이 부분은 이 div로, 이 grid는 이 div로 채운다를 알려줌</li>\n<li>시각화된 형태로 보여준다</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.father {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 200px);\n  grid-template-rows: 100px repeat(2, 200px) 100px;\n  grid-template-areas:\n    &quot;header header header header&quot;\n    &quot;content content content nav&quot;\n    &quot;content content content nav&quot;\n    &quot;footer footer footer footer&quot;;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"gird-area\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gird-area\" aria-label=\"gird area permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gird-area</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>각 div의 css값에 <code class=\"language-text\">grid-area</code>값을 부여해서, 어떤 grid area를 해당 div가 차지할지를 정할 수 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">    .header {\n    background: peru;\n    grid-area: header;\n    }\n\n    .content {\n    background: skyblue;\n    grid-area: content;\n    }</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"grid-template-colums-repeate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grid-template-colums-repeate\" aria-label=\"grid template colums repeate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>grid-template-colums :repeate</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">repeat</code>를 활용하면 컬럼 값을 여러번 수기로 안넣어도 됨</li>\n<li>예시</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.father {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 200px);\n  grid-template-rows: 100px repeat(2, 200px) 100px;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"24-rows-and-columns\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#24-rows-and-columns\" aria-label=\"24 rows and columns permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[2.4] Rows and Columns</h1>\n<h3 id=\"grid-rowcolumn-start\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#grid-rowcolumn-start\" aria-label=\"grid rowcolumn start permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>grid-row/column-start</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>grid-area, grid-template-area를 사용하지 않고, 어떤 <code class=\"language-text\">line</code>부터 어떤 <code class=\"language-text\">line</code>까지 해당 item을 stretch 시킬 것인지를 부여함</li>\n<li>더 나은 방법!</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">        .header {\n        background: peru;\n        grid-column-start: 1;\n        grid-column-end: 5;\n        }\n\n        .content {\n        background: skyblue;\n        grid-column-start: 1;\n        grid-column-end: 4;\n        grid-row-start: 2;\n        grid-row-end: 4;\n        }</code></pre></div>","excerpt":"2.2 CSS Grid Basic Concepts Grid Grid가 나온 이유? 각 item 간의 간격 등을 grid 형태로 깔끔하게, 정돈되게 관리할 수 있음 flex box에서는 개별 item 간의 간격을 각각 조정해줘야 하는 귀찮음 Grid는…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/TIL_49_210310/#22-css-grid-basic-concepts\">2.2 CSS Grid Basic Concepts</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_49_210310/#grid\">Grid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_49_210310/#1-grid-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">1. Grid 방법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_49_210310/#2-grid%EC%9D%98-column-%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">2. Grid의 column 사이즈 설정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_49_210310/#3-grid-row-%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88-%EC%84%B1%EC%A0%95\">3. Grid row 사이즈 성정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_49_210310/#4-column-row-%EA%B0%84%EC%9D%98-%EA